languages.text: "I saw you near the marketplace. What were you doing there?"
languages.original_text: "Я видел{mf||а} тебя у торговища. Что ты там делал?"

traits.locale_text: "I saw you near the marketplace. What were you doing there?"
"I have seen you near the marketplace. If you are in charge, why did you not stand up for one of your workers?"
"I saw you near the marketplace. What were you doing there?"
"I saw you near the marketplace. If you are in charge, why did you not stand up for that worker of yours?"
"I saw you near the marketplace. What were you doing there?"
"I saw you near the marketplace. What were you doing there?"
"I saw you near the marketplace. What were you doing there?"
"I saw you near the marketplace. What were you doing there?"

languages.text: «Le vi cerca del mercado. ¿Qué hacía allí?».
languages.original_text: "I saw you near the marketplace. What were you doing there?"

traits.locale_text: «Le vi cerca del mercado. ¿Qué hacía allí?».
«Le vi cerca del mercado. Si está al mando, ¿por qué no defendió a ese trabajador suyo?».

languages.text: 「市場付近でお前を見かけた。あそこで何をしていたのだ？」
languages.original_text: "I saw you near the marketplace. What were you doing there?"

traits.locale_text: 「市場付近でお前を見かけた。あそこで何をしていたのだ？」
「市場付近でお前を見かけた。責任者だというのなら、なぜあの労働者のために立ち上がらなかったのだ？」

languages.text: “我之前在市场那边见到过你，你当时在那里干什么呢？”
languages.original_text: "I saw you near the marketplace. What were you doing there?"

traits.locale_text: “我之前在市场那边见到过你，你当时在那里干什么呢？”
“我之前在市场那边见到过你。既然你是这里的负责人，你当时为什么没有站出来，维护你手下的工人？”

languages.text: "Ich habe Euch in der Nähe des Marktplatzes gesehen. Was habt Ihr dort gemacht?"
languages.original_text: "I saw you near the marketplace. What were you doing there?"

traits.locale_text: "Ich habe Euch in der Nähe des Marktplatzes gesehen. Was habt Ihr dort gemacht?"
"Ich habe Euch beim Marktplatz gesehen. Wenn Ihr das Sagen habt, warum habt Ihr Euch dann nicht für Euren Arbeiter eingesetzt?"

languages.text: « Je vous ai déjà vu près du marché. Que faisiez-vous là-bas ? »
languages.original_text: "I saw you near the marketplace. What were you doing there?"

traits.locale_text: « Je vous ai déjà vu près du marché. Que faisiez-vous là-bas ? »
« Je vous ai déjà vu près du marché. Si vous êtes vraiment aux commandes ici, pourquoi ne pas avoir défendu votre ouvrier ? »

languages.text: "Seni pazar yerinin yakınlarında gördüm. Orada ne yapıyordun?"
languages.original_text: "I saw you near the marketplace. What were you doing there?"
